    decisions, and it can support prioritization without needing a heavy model upfront. If helpful, I may also add query-text
    similarity as an extra feature, but I want to start with the structured signals first."
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 2. The question: decision, action, cost of a wrong call\n\n*What decision does your work improve? Who acts on it? What does a wrong recommendation cost?*"
